{"tid":1837723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[報應]今次算唔算近20年最接近支爆，天滅中共，全黨死清光","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T03:33:37.000Z","uid":31215,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df2a46d1a1182aa3c417e98313dd4faf52d794f5","tid":1837723,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"個天都可憐香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話上訴蒙面法<br />\n個疫症搞到人人唔蒙面唔得<br />\n<br />\n話高鐵人多唔使申報<br />\n就由高鐵運一件落黎<br />\n<br />\n林順潮一話樂觀<br />\n睇眼都有武漢肺炎病人摸上門，完全唔撚關事<br />\n<br />\n班藍絲小粉紅話信黨，就俾黨出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警總又疑似中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫劇本都寫唔到咁岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果再巧合啲<br />\n死返兩件黑警<br />\n運多幾十件去德國，佢地咁大愛應該可以接收<br />\n英國都唔可以少，以佢地同中國嘅交情應該會幫手<br />\n中國再爆多幾個鎮<br />\n咁就真係俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec04831ee8e469cb38a8e16114f28208ee89635","tid":1837723,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1eca935f309a53c8c8660626fc6dc55e73924a3","tid":1837723,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:53:33.000Z","msg":"一半半，佢地一直做唔好，  疫症可以係早期預防，但無做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門！！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以